author: WCAX News
title: West Wardsboro woman charged with DUI
text:
BROOKFIELD, Vt. - A West Wardsboro woman faces drunk driving charges after police say they found her behind the wheel when she was three times over the legal limit to drive.
Police say they saw Josie Walbridge, 36, driving very slowly and swerving on Interstate 89 northbound in Brookfield Thursday night.
Police say she blew a 0.253 and was arrested for DUI.
